"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pU-IX_aeNsAC56wqR2xe3.png?height=457&width=689)\\n\\n原创作者Source：Kinjal.mirror.xyz\\n\\n翻译整理：Kevinmhj.eth\\n\\n（里面的文章内容，我会找时间进行一一翻译，并发布在Mirror上的）\\n\\n[https://kinjal.mirror.xyz/eD3-Sgv2h50j-kwjHQCOnwqMKqSLTfnrqrtNypU-P5k](https://kinjal.mirror.xyz/eD3-Sgv2h50j-kwjHQCOnwqMKqSLTfnrqrtNypU-P5k)\\n\\n### DAO入门101：\\n\\n* [A Beginner's Guide to DAOs](https://linda.mirror.xyz/Vh8K4leCGEO06_qSGx-vS5lvgUqhqkCz9ut81WwCP2o)\\n* [Everything You Need to Know about DAOs](https://foundation.app/blog/everything-you-need-to-know-about-daos)\\n* [DAOs, DACs, DAs, and more](https://blog.ethereum.org/2014/05/06/daos-dacs-das-and-more-an-incomplete-terminology-guide/)\\n* [An Introduction to DAOs](https://medium.com/metawork/an-introduction-to-daos-782e3817e2cd)\\n* [The DAO of DAOs](https://www.notboring.co/p/the-dao-of-daos)\\n\\n### 为什么需要DAO？\\n\\n* [Crypto Commons](https://blog.usejournal.com/crypto-commons-da602fb98138)\\n* [Power to the Person](https://www.notboring.co/p/power-to-the-person)\\n* [The Ownership Economy](https://variant.fund/the-ownership-economy-crypto-and-consumer-software/)\\n* [DAOs of Tomorrow](https://twitter.com/albiverse/status/1372263045842485257)\\n* [NFT Value Capture Equation](https://coopahtroopa.mirror.xyz/A16NP2XXi9RdHptfdF9WHR0Xq_E1XDmUgMwPmJYOG7w)\\n\\n### 治理\\n\\n* [Blockchain Governance](https://medium.com/@FEhrsam/blockchain-governance-programming-our-future-c3bfe30f2d74)\\n* [How do we make Decentralized Decisions](https://medium.com/the-caring-network-company/how-we-make-decentralized-decisions-ad869417b772)\\n* [The Most Important Scarce Resource is Legitimacy](https://t.co/vLCznqP1Lv?amp=1)\\n* [On-chain Vote-Buying and the Rise of Dark DAOs](https://hackingdistributed.com/2018/07/02/on-chain-vote-buying/)\\n* [Life of a Protocol Politician](https://newsletter.banklesshq.com/p/the-life-of-a-protocol-politician)\\n\\n### 金库/货币化\\n\\n* [Unlocking the Treasury](https://sukernik.medium.com/unlocking-the-treasury-483aeea01001)\\n* [The Future of On-Chain Treasury Management](https://newsletter.banklesshq.com/p/how-daos-should-approach-treasury)\\n* [A Crisis in Protocol Treasury Management](https://messari.io/article/a-crisis-in-protocol-treasury-management-and-how-to-solve-it?utm_source=robertotalamas&utm_medium=tweet&utm_campaign=protocol-treasury-manangement)\\n* [A Media Ownership Model](https://darkstar.mirror.xyz/8p0qPpLDPNkV6Bb4ObfSCdR2PKAN0Gz9tWTnGq7ikRY)\\n* [The Rise of Micro-economies](https://coopahtroopa.mirror.xyz/gWY6Kfebs9wHdfoZZswfiLTBVzfKiyFaIwNf2q8JpgI)\\n* [The Creator Attribution Ratio](https://creativekitchen.so/penguins/The-current-NFT-debate-is-a-false-choice-tIATu)\\n* [Exploring the Social Token Revolution](https://andrewsteinwold.substack.com/p/-exploring-the-social-token-revolution)\\n\\n### 创作者们 & 未来的工作\\n\\n* [NFTs and the Future of Work](https://www.drorpoleg.com/nfts-and-the-future-of-work/)\\n* [Blockchains Unlock Institutions with Internet Scale](https://medium.com/blockchain-capital-blog/blockchains-unlock-institutions-with-internet-scale-b5af9d930e1e)\\n* [Slow Death of the Firm](https://thecontrol.co/the-slow-death-of-the-firm-1bd6cc81286b)\\n* [Crypto’s Creator Model](https://medium.com/blockchain-capital-blog/cryptos-creator-model-bee11024336b)\\n* [1000 true fans? Try 100](https://a16z.com/2020/02/06/100-true-fans/)\\n\\n### 怎么“DAO”？\\n\\n* [How to create a DAOs](https://newsletter.banklesshq.com/p/how-to-create-a-bankless-dao)\\n* [Tips for Creators getting into Crypto](https://p.mirror.xyz/WQQywdjjfnksMRPMaNKBMxPBqfE5k8nL6pCLe1roGyw)\\n* [How to Structure a Protocol's Treasury](https://shreyashariharan.com/2021/03/14/how-to-structure-a-protocols-treasury/)\\n* [Come for the creator, stay for the economy](https://p.mirror.xyz/1EpvJwUpx_KlRcHOKLNqADEkwHL_Z1ZYKobF2uLwgBg)\\n* [Governance Legos](https://medium.com/tally-blog/governance-legos-6559f2234a3a)\\n\\n### 分析\\n\\n* [DeepDAO](https://deepdao.io/#/deepdao/dashboard)\\n* [Tally Governance Dashboards](https://www.withtally.com/)\\n\\n### 刊物和订阅\\n\\n* [Darkstar](https://darkstar.mirror.xyz/)\\n* [Albi's Newsletter](https://albiverse.blog/)\\n* [Forefront](https://forefront.market/newsletter)\\n* [Crypto X Creator Economy](https://p.mirror.xyz/)\\n* [Woong Joon Ian’s Pacenotes](https://medium.com/@joonian)\\n* [Stateless](https://stateless.boardroom.info/)\\n* [Gardens](https://gardens.substack.com/)\\n* [Monkey with a Typewriter](https://frogmonkee.substack.com/)\\n\\n### 额外的DAO相关资源\\n\\n* [DAO Tools & Resources](https://www.notion.so/DAO-Tools-and-Resources-cecc1368c32041fc89515a63f00bae28)\\n* [Not Boring DAO Links](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1oBMUWawlRcVFYwGXsC5UDrcET3VSXZ_bGAHCViWx8-g/edit)\\n* [DAO Creation & Design](https://daotalk.org/t/resource-list-dao-creation-design/522)\\n* [Awesome DAOs](https://github.com/DAOresearch/awesome-daos/blob/master/README.md)\\n* [DAO Legal Resources](https://hackmd.io/@LinXule/BywFKmp6L)\\n* [a16z NFT Canon](https://a16z.com/2021/04/02/nfts-readings-resources/)\\n* [House of DAOs](https://wiki.metagame.wtf/docs/great-houses/house-of-daos)\\n* [Best DAO Tools](https://app.yup.io/collections/best-dao-tools/YBdtqHg)\",\"timestamp\":1641281319,\"title\":\"DAO&创作者：从零入门的学习资源\"},\"digest\":\"E8c2iM_aXmfPOZnlbMoetVyBB3HrveRh4nGTN8Uqwlg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7C42B99A1A8F2eC5201eaA98d10e187f3957a36a\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"yaEcRlamCDHYXnK7XUNH4qeBG_LECM2eYRdAvFYLEGs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yPSBo5ZCnA1ain7a8R6jMKsd0Xneagjzaccfm0plcXg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"9HThNZkyd3Lyq79WWmoVTOiebxpMnabJxliyHLQmzFnf63G4ld8Zc0TQxZy-sR4wOWHv3DwiP-6tyxbJPoNiPQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb8c14b35d3f5353a597a83c07d7cd772b738e537b71dc8c197e63869a466269c050feed684c89da0bae919010757d4e6dc14b5669aa21329139c29faa503b3681c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publi